<br>
Ignore most of damage that the shout does by offsetting it against a garrote!<br>
<br>
Is Elaa an accountant?  Obviously the DD doesnt count as damage because its a charitable contribution.  Ah, lets not note that its ranged damage because we consider only melee combat.  Lets not consider the front loading for compound interest.<br>
<br>
Lets write off 2% raw damage against reduced (but not by anywhere near 2%) style damage (perhapse the records were destroyed in a flood).<br>
<br>
The only time that the DD has a DPS of 3.15 is if the fight lasts an exact multiple of 20 seconds.  Most fights are decided well within 20 seconds (group fights - duels vary a great deal but snare kiting works well with the DDs).<br>
<br>
Lets not account for the way people actualy fight most of the time (hit and run or jousting), lets not make anything of the fact that you very rarely go below half endurance in a stand up knock down fight with another assassin (and rarely have stand up knock down fights with anyone else).<br>
<br>
The 63 DD is ranged, instacast, and front loaded.  The end cost is imaterial in 90% of fights and in any case you can cast the DD when OOE (unlike infiltrators or SBs who cannot use a ranged attack when OOE).<br>
<br>
Front loaded: if the fight lasts 10 seconds (i.e. someone is assissting the NS to kill) its effective dps is 6.3 if the fight lasts only 5 seconds (e.g. a typical hit and run: PA, CD on a caster) its effective DPS is 12.6.  If the fight lasts only 1 hit then its effective DPS is 63.<br>
<br>
Lets put some weighting on this and say that 1 in ten fights lasts exactly 20 seconds, 5 in ten last 5 seconds and 4 in ten last 10 seconds.  That gives an adjusted Effective DPS of 9.4 for the shout.  5.9% more total DPS than an infiltrator.<br>
<br>
So the nightshade has the best offence of any assassin by a significant margin.  The nightshade has two more offence RAs than either of the other two assassins.<br>
<br>
Defence:<br>
Your analysis takes only stats into consideration and not the smallness of Lurikeens which is an important defensive feature.<br>
<br>
Your analysis does not take buffs into consideration.  A well buffed and equiped NS will have arround 250 con (may need Aug con 1 I don't know hibi buffs) and the benefit of con drops off by about half after that point.  So the defensive stat advantages that a Briton enjoys are far less significant than your analysis would indicate.<br>
<br>
The only physical stat that is dificult to get to 250 is Quickness because there is no base buff and few items.  Infils who don't spend starting points in qui will have dificulty hitting this cap, no NS will have trouble.<br>
<br>
You fail to remark that no assassin has 'good' defence and relies on tactics and competant support for survival in many situations.  Hibernia has superior support classes (Warden, Bard, Druid).<br>
<br>
Conclusion:<br>
The nightshade is superior by a significant margin, mostly due to the potent shout spell which not only out damages every other assassin in the overwhelming majority of battles but has multiple utility for disrupting an oponant.  Night shades have stats well suited to the role of assassination and benefit most from potent buffs which are often available in Hibernia. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uaach.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aach</A> at: 8/3/02 8:48:45 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uravnnevermoor.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ravn Nevermoor</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/4/02 11:38:57 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3874.topic&index=15>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Refuted</span><hr size=1> I've become more and more convinced that NSs are just as balanced as the rest of the assassins out there. <p>Ravn Nevermoor<Br>50 infiltrator<Br>Aeonian Prophecy<BR>NERF PBAE AND BUFFBOTS!!!</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uolmoss.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Olmoss</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_bluespot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/4/02 2:58:25 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3874.topic&index=16>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Refuted</span><hr size=1>  I love guys that dont play nightshades telling us how wonderful we are..<br>
