As for Nightshades being defensively weaker, this is somewhat true. They have a little less hps, but evade a little more. Nightshades have the same hp table as other realm's assassins, but Hibernian races have generally lower con. They high dex, and very high quickness. Quickness = dmg. Which you didn't factor in when you mentioned about Nightshades offensive strength. We don't see Highlander tanks complaining about having lesser str/hps than Troll tanks. They live with it, knowing they have more dex and quickness to make up for it.<br>
